_sText:
office deathmatch with dmm elements. (one wall but still great looking)
Even tho this is a deathmatch map, it should work well with just normal css "non-objectiveless-no-respawn" gamemode.
might lag on older pcs.
Includes:
-Nav file for bots
-32 player limit
-A LOT of breakable glass cs_office style!

Should be bug free but im not 100% sure.
i got a lot of inspiration from the original cs_office.
And if you encounter a bug, screenshot it and send it to me.
Have fun! :D
